<runspec version="MOVES5.0.1">
	<description><![CDATA[Crankcase Extended Idle Exhaust (process 17) at County (SINGLE) scale — non-vacuous variant.

Process 17 crankcase extended-idle exhaust is proportional to extended-idle exhaust
(process 90). Extended-idle activity (hotellingHours) is populated at hourID=7 only.
This variant runs at hour 7 with county-scale hotellingHours so that crankcase
extended-idle exhaust is non-vacuous.

Requires scale-input directory with hotellingHours.parquet (county hotelling activity,
hour 7). Snapshot captured with canonical MOVES 5.0.1 against a county input DB
containing hotellingHoursPerDay.]]></description>
